Use: Fashion nearby garbage into a sphere and launch it into the sky. After 3 sec of gathering momentum the sphere crashes into the targeted location dealing 1.7 million Physical damage split between all enemies in the area. (2 Min Cooldown)

This effect's duration is increased by up to 40 sec based on when you were last imbued.
